-- An imported ADT crossing the module boundary.  The entry defines an
-- arg-position interface (`Code`) with an impl AT this imported type AND at the
-- PRIMITIVE `Int`; the primitive-receiver call is the case E4 unlocks on the
-- multi-module emit path (an `Int` immediate carries no cell tag, so pre-E4 it
-- fell to arg-tag dispatch → census-B gap #2).
public export data Widget = Widget
